data.description: Spacious ranch home on large lot backing to large field and trees.  3 bedroom, 2 baths with walk-in showers, large open concept kitchen/living/dining room, plus large primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom, additional large potential 4th bedroom, and patio with French doors and whirlpool tub. Living room features electric fireplace.  New Trex deck, fully fenced backyard.  Great location for schools, shopping and easy freeway access. Low maintenance front yard with evergreens, fruit trees, and berry bushes.
data.whatILove: The open concept living area, plus 2 other large rooms, patio with whirlpool tub, Trex deck and rhododendrons in  back.  Peaceful and safe neighborhood.
